title: Two kayakers die in New Zealand while on Monash University exchange trip
text:
Two kayakers die in New Zealand while... Two kayakers die in New Zealand while on Monash University exchange trip Next Story Prev Story 3 hrs ago Read more: The Age 
Two kayakers who were on an exchange trip from Monash University to New Zealand have died after a wave hit them on Lake Tekapo. Two kayakers who died on Lake Tekapo on Friday were part of an exchange group visiting New Zealand with Melbourne's Monash University.   The Age.
